rows.label: fev11_590_170_msg0001
rows.name:
Come on. We shouldn't keep our old
friend waiting any longer. Time for us
to make a move.

rows.label: fev11_590_170_msg0002
rows.name:
The Iiran womb, he said. So is that
going to be inside the titan's belly?

rows.label: fev11_590_170_msg0004
rows.name: This isn't the time for games, you know.

rows.label: fev11_590_170_msg0005
rows.name:
It would have to be a cavity of
considerable size for Seiryu to
fit inside.

rows.label: fev11_590_170_msg0007
rows.name:
We should head for the front entrance,
then turn left. That way we'll come to a
back gate.

rows.label: fev11_590_170_msg0008
rows.name:
If we head down past there, it should
take us to the womb's entrance.

rows.label: fev11_590_170_msg0009
rows.name:
OK. We'd better catch up to Seiryuu-san
then!
